	(379,1,'2014-02-24 19:26:46','2014-02-24 19:26:46','<h1 class=\"entry-title\">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>\r\n<div class=\"peach_background\">\r\n<ul id=\"lstFAQ\">\r\n	<li><a href=\"#Use\">How can I benefit from ProspectNow?</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"#Cost\">How much does it cost?</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"#trial\">Is there a free trial?</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"#Property\">What types of properties are covered in the database?</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"#content\">Where does all this data come from?</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"#update\">How often do you update your data?</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"#internet\">What differentiates ProspectNow from generic list brokers on the Internet?</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"#sign\">How do I sign up for the service?</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>How can I benefit from ProspectNow?<a id=\"Use\" name=\"Use\"></a></strong>\r\nProspectNow can increase your sales volume, and therefore your bottom line, by enabling you to contact more property owners with less effort. It is unique in that ProspectNow combines property data, phone numbers and contact management software in a single tool to create the best property ownership lists in the industry. <a href=\"http://www.prospectnow.com/index.php?page=mailinglist\">Click here</a> to see what you can do with ProspectNow\r\n\r\n<strong>How much does it cost?</strong><a name=\"Cost\"></a>\r\nPlans start $89 a month per user for one county and additional counties are $10/mo. Bulk plans are also available that grant nationwide access at discounted rates.\r\n\r\n<strong>Is there a free trial?</strong><a name=\"trial\"></a>\r\nAny potential subscriber is encouraged to create a free account, which will provide access to property ownership lists in the county of their choice. This trial account will showcase the ProspectNow software and search tools, allowing you to see how many property type records are available within your marketplace. Building owner details, however, are only available to paying subscribers or you can also try our free 3 day trial which requires your credit card information. The system will not bill you for 3 days, and if you choose to cancel prior to the end of 3rd day, you will not be billed at all. Otherwise you will be billed every 30 days. Thanks for trying us out! <a href=\"http://www.prospectnow.com/search-commercial-real-estate.html\">Click here</a> to create your free account.\r\n\r\n<strong>What types of properties are covered in the database?</strong><a name=\"Property\"></a>\r\nThe ProspectNow database covers multifamily, retail, office and industrial property types. The database also contains 30 million business owners and tenants nationwide.\r\n\r\n<strong>Where does all this data come from?</strong><a name=\"content\"></a>\r\nAll property ownership information is public domain, and every county keeps a record of this information for every building within its parameters.  The challenge many professionals face is that pieces of this information, such as a phone numbers, owner names behind LLCs, and tenants may not be provided in the county records. That\'s where ProspectNow comes in. We do the research for you to find the phone numbers and other information that is absent from county records.  The resulting property ownership lists are one of the most effective tools you can employ to get more listings.\r\n\r\n<strong>How often do you update your data?</strong>\r\n<a name=\"update\"></a>The ProspectNow database is updated every 30 days. There are a few counties that are updated on an annual basis, but most are updated monthly.\r\n\r\n<strong>What differentiates ProspectNow from generic list brokers on the Internet?</strong> <a name=\"internet\"></a>\r\nProspectNow is designed for commercial real estate professionals. It\'s the only product that integrates phone numbers, property and owner information and a contact manager into one system. You don\'t have to search through multiple systems to fill in all the information you need on a property or owner. Therefore, you can contact more owners in less time, resulting in more deals.\r\n\r\n<strong>How do I sign up for the service?</strong><a name=\"sign\"></a>\r\nYou can sign up online or by calling 888-956-9998. We accept credit cards or eChecks.<a href=\"/search-commercial-real-estate/\">Click Here</a> to sign up','FAQ- property ownership lists','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-revision-v1','','','2014-02-24 19:26:46','2014-02-24 19:26:46','',11,'http://adarsh.prospectnow.com/11-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
