nd organized within ProspectNow.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6 \"><a class=\"testimonialDemo\" onclick=\"loadYoutube(\'HuecYqSkuDo\');return false;\" href=\"#\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#myModal\"> </a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row demo-entry\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-10 col-md-offset-1\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6 hidden-xs\"><a class=\"testimonialDemo\" onclick=\"loadYoutube(\'HL3Fuf-n848\');return false;\" href=\"#\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#myModal\"> </a></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\">\r\n<h1>Activity Tracking</h1>\r\nIf you manage a team of users, we provide you everything you need to monitor and team activity.  Track your team\'s deals from initial contact to close.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row demo-entry\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-10 col-md-offset-1\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\">\r\n<h1>Mobile App Demo</h1>\r\nProperty information wherever you are. If you are driving by a property and see it would be a great fit for a client, simply access the info on ProspectNow on your phone. Enter a note and even call the owner while in the field.\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6 hidden-lg\"><a class=\"testimonialDemo\" onclick=\"loadYoutube(\'sMbvYQ3DCcc\');return false;\" href=\"#\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#myModal\"> </a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row demo-entry\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-10 col-md-offset-1\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12 align-center\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"/search-commercial-real-estate\">Sign Up Now</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">\r\n@media (max-width: 500px) {\r\n.testimonialDemo{\r\n      width:100%;\r\n	background: url(\'/wp-content/themes/prospect-now/images/demonstrationRollover2.png\') bottom ;\r\nmax-width:430px;\r\n\r\n}\r\n.testimonial